### Login as CUSTOMER (session cookie)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "YourPasswordHere"
}

### Get cart (empty or with lines)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/customer/cart

### Add product — replace PRODUCT_ID with a real active product id from GET /api/v1/catalog/products
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/customer/cart/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": "PRODUCT_ID",
  "quantity": 2
}

### Update line quantity — replace ITEM_ID from cart response
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/v1/customer/cart/items/ITEM_ID
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 1
}

### Remove line
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/v1/customer/cart/items/ITEM_ID
